<P><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1+ letters">y this time <HI>M.
Magdalen</HI> was come <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 word"> again to
the <HI>Sepulcher</HI> where the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1+ letters">r
Women had &s;tay'd for her, and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 word">
the <HI>Angel</HI> &s;peaks to them, and
<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1+ letters">s them of another gro&s;s
Ab&s;urdity, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1+ letters">ebukes them for it,
<HI>Why &s;eek ye the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1+ letters">g among&s;t
the dead?</HI> Why him who <PB N="176" REF="215"> is the Son of the living God,
the Prince of Life, who hath Life in him&s;elf, and who is Life it &s;elf,
